<div class="content_box">
	<div class="content_text_wrapper front_page">
		<h2 class="content_heading">It's Easy... and It's Free!</h2>

        <ul class="bullet">
            <li class="content">Browse a wishlist and donate items</li>
            <li class="content">Post items you can spare and they will be matched with an
                                         organization in need</li>
            <li class="content">Make a financial donation to a shelter of your choice</li>
        </ul>
	</div>
</div>

<br/>
<br/>

<div class="content_box">
	<div class="content_text_wrapper front_page">
		<h2 class="content_heading">Anyone Can Help!</h2>
		
		<p class="content inline">Local shelter's top wishlist item is blankets?</p>
		<p class="content inline bold">Donate them!</p>
		<br/>
		<p class="content inline">Puppy grew too large for his collar?</p>
		<p class="content inline bold">Post it for donation!</p>
		<br/>
		<p class="content inline">Extra birthday cash?</p>
		<p class="content inline bold">Donate it to your favorite organization!</p>
		<br/>
		<p class="content inline">Any donation, large or small, can benefit animals in shelters and
						   rescues.</p>
		<br/>
		<br/>
		<!-- The last <p> tag of .content_wrapper MUST be inline (or else bottom margin breaks): -->
		<p class="content inline">Research shows that shelters don't often get the supplies they need and it is
						   the goal of Spared to help make this happen.<br/> 
						   By involving the community and streamlining the way organizations get 
						   supplies, volunteers are less bogged down by daily operations,<br/> 
						   and animals get the love and care they need. Getting rid of those unused pet 
						   supplies also ensures a cleaner garage!</p>
	</div>
</div>

<br/>
<br/>

<div class="content_box">
	<div class="content_text_wrapper front_page">
		<h2 class="content_heading">Who is Eligible?</h2>
		
		<p class="content">Though we aim to help all animal organizations, there are a few registration
						   qualifications<br/> 
						   to ensure integrity. To register an organization for donations, the 
						   organization must:</p>
        <ul class="bullet">
            <li class="content">Be nonprofit [registered or non-registered]</li>
            <li class="content">Have a physical address and facility</li>
            <li class="content">Be willing to take care of shipping costs and/or transportation of items</li>
        </ul>
		<br/>
		<!-- The last <p> tag of .content_wrapper MUST be inline (or else bottom margin breaks): -->
		<p class="content inline">For full eligibility requirements,</p>
		<%= link_to 'register now!', 'register', :class => 'login_link inline', :rel => 'facebox' %>
	</div>
</div>